name: Christabel Menns
description: am here looking for serious relationship. I like walking at night admiring city lights, playing billiard and making sexy photos. I’m always active and I enjoy this life to the fullest. I love traveling. You can find me on a sunny beach in some warm country basking in the sun or swimming.. Hey I think I’m just perfect for a sport that doesn’t require clothes. And of course I love taking care of myself because I know that men love with their eyes. And I want you to love me! You know, almost every young girl wants to have a pony. When I was a kid, I didn’t want a pony, I wanted a horse. But that dream never came true.. Even now, when I became a lady, I still want to learn riding. Maybe someday you could give me some lessons? I hope our interests are the same )
